        Selling a Renovated Property in Brisbane: Council Approvals and What Sellers Must Disclose
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Unapproved renovations transfer with the property. Understanding your disclosure obligations before you list protects you and builds buyer confidence.
      </p>
